pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "#FFFFFF"
elements:
  - elementId: page-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 40, 1120, 40]
    content:
      fontSize: 32
      color: "#1E293B"
      fontFamily: "Liter, MiSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>亚太区复合增长率达15%，24个月内跨越盈亏平衡点</strong></p>

  - elementId: title-line
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [80, 86, 1120, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "#E2E8F0"

  # Vertical divider
  - elementId: grid-v-line
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [640, 106, 0, 540]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "#E2E8F0"

  # Horizontal divider
  - elementId: grid-h-line
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [80, 376, 1120, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "#E2E8F0"

  # Q1: Context (top-left)
  - elementId: q1-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 112, 200, 20]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      color: "#64748B"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: false
      text: CONTEXT

  - elementId: q1-number
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 140, 520, 56]
    content:
      fontSize: 48
      color: "#B45309"
      fontFamily: "Liter, MiSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>$2,320B</p>

  - elementId: q1-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 206, 520, 140]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "#1E293B"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      wrap: true
      text: |
        <p>全球SaaS市场2024年规模达$2,320亿，中国渗透率仅10%，对比美国62%存在巨大追赶空间。政策驱动+技术拐点双重催化。</p>

  # Q2: Objective (top-right)
  - elementId: q2-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [680, 112, 200, 20]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      color: "#64748B"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: false
      text: OBJECTIVE

  - elementId: q2-number
    elementType: text
    bounds: [680, 140, 520, 56]
    content:
      fontSize: 48
      color: "#B45309"
      fontFamily: "Liter, MiSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>$25M ARR</p>

  - elementId: q2-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [680, 206, 500, 140]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "#1E293B"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      wrap: true
      text: |
        <p>三年内实现ARR从$3.8M增长至$25M。客户数从200+扩展至800+。净收入留存率维持128%以上。</p>

  # Q3: Path (bottom-left)
  - elementId: q3-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 396, 200, 20]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      color: "#64748B"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: false
      text: PATH

  - elementId: q3-number
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 424, 520, 56]
    content:
      fontSize: 48
      color: "#B45309"
      fontFamily: "Liter, MiSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>3 Phases</p>

  - elementId: q3-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 490, 520, 140]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "#1E293B"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      wrap: true
      text: |
        <p>Phase 1: 产品市场验证（$1M ARR）。Phase 2: 规模化增长（$5M ARR）。Phase 3: 市场领导地位（$25M ARR）。</p>

  # Q4: ROI (bottom-right)
  - elementId: q4-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [680, 396, 200, 20]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      color: "#64748B"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      wrap: false
      text: EXPECTED ROI

  - elementId: q4-number
    elementType: text
    bounds: [680, 424, 520, 56]
    content:
      fontSize: 48
      color: "#B45309"
      fontFamily: "Liter, MiSans"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>5.2x Return</p>

  - elementId: q4-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [680, 490, 500, 140]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "#1E293B"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      lineHeight: 1.5
      wrap: true
      text: |
        <p>本轮融资$8M，18个月达成盈亏平衡。预计3年投资回报5.2倍。毛利率从55%提升至72%。</p>

  - elementId: page-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [1150, 680, 50, 24]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      color: "#64748B"
      fontFamily: "QuattrocentoSans, MiSans"
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: "04"
